section.title: Description
section.p: This class contains all other case identifiers for this case used in ICH ICSR electronic transmissions.

stentry.p: "Provide[s] all other case identifiers for this case used in ICH ICSR electronic transmissions. If the case has been received from another sender, all other case identifiers ... should be retransmitted." - ICH E2B(R3), C.1.9.1.r.2.

"Provide[s] all sources (organisation’s name) of electronic transmissions for this case. If the case has been received from another sender, all other case identifiers ... should be retransmitted." - ICH E2B(R3), C.1.9.1.r.1.
